Articles.Content: Floor 677: The horde of Swinubs are still running towards you and chasing you.
Floor 678 is the flamethrower shop. You're in luck now.
Floor 679: Umm... you wanna watch your step as you can see its a very large hole that leads to the first floor....Better hurry i can feel a strong breeze coming in.
Floor 679: You see a bunch of birds having war using RC vehicles.

Jebediah rides his rocket through the hole in floor 679, forces you into it, and then past the bird war up to:

Floor 680: where you are caught in the middle of "Polar Warfare 3, Christmas Miracle"

Edited December 31, 2013 by Noname117
Floor 680: The RC Vehicle warzone becomes a colony of the Swinub Empire.
Floor 681:Oh we got trouble fellas with that warning sign saying "Danger waterfall ahead" leap onto percy before it is to late!
Floor 682: You hear the Swinub's screams and cries of mercy as they get slaughtered 2 floors below you by a unknown creature...
Floor 682: well your in a train chase scenelike in lone ranger ,and not to forget this song playing out loud as you get to the next floor.

Floor 683: You see a large hoard of prime numbers wandering the halls, and assuming they were lost in the teleporter incident a few hundred floors ago, you direct them to floor 777 and proceed to the next floor.
Floor 684: The Saturn-V from a few hundred floors ago is now lifting off. You run
Floor 685: Jebidiah Kerman fighting The Kraken!
Floor 686 - You find a hungry bob kerman in a really steep pit, you throw your sandwich in.
Floor 687: Pyramid head charges at you and you slam the close door button.
Floor 689: IS THAT AN ELEVATOR??? Umm. no it's only Bob's newst invention called "The Block"
Floor 690: You try to climb the launch clamp...
Floor 691 - Nothing really special on this floor, but as you peer out the window, bob is seen piloting the "Zephyr" RCS lander.
Floor 692 - The abyss is on this floor, which you stare into, and the abyss stares back.
Floor 693:

Floor 694: you stare out the window and get scared because of the height, Jeb pushes you with a massive SRB contraption that he somehow got into the building ,you fall down but Bob saves you with his newly built VTOL craft and puts you one floor higher
Floor 695: Nothing to see here... Just move along...
Floor 696, you see a supply cabinet with oxygen bottles and masks for those proceeding much higher.
697: Flat Earth Society headquarters
698: You come across a large potato salad.
